  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    Congratulations on obtaining your Sheriff Court decree through Simple Procedure. However, a decree alone does not automatically result in payment. If the defender does not pay voluntarily within 14 days, you will need to take <strong>diligence</strong> (enforcement action) to recover the money owed.
  </p>
